         </p>
         <div class="flex items-center justify-center lg:justify-start gap-6 pt-8 border-t border-slate-100">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full text-white flex items-center justify-center font-black text-sm shadow-md" style="background-color: var(--color-indigo-900)">QA</div>
              <div class="text-left">
