            </svg>
          </div>

          <div class="relative z-10">
            <div class="absolute -left-10 md:-left-14 top-0 w-1.5 h-full rounded-full" style="background-color: var(--color-amber-400); box-shadow: 0 0 20px var(--color-amber-400)"></div>
            <h3 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black mb-6 tracking-tight" style="color: var(--color-amber-400)">The Oral Blockchain</h3>
            
            <p class="text-lg md:text-2xl leading-relaxed m-0 font-medium" style="color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);">
              "The Isnad is a decentralized human ledger. Each Ijazah holder is a node of truth. If one person tries to alter the Word, the entire network identifies the anomaly instantly."
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <section id="s2" class="scroll-mt-32 border-t border-slate-100 pt-10">
          <h2>II. The Science of the Isnad (The Chain)</h2>
          <p>The <strong>Isnad</strong> is the list of names documented on an Ijazah certificate. It serves as the student's pedagogical lineage: "I learned from Sheikh X, who learned from Sheikh Y, who learned from Imam Z..." back to the <strong>Sahaba (Companions)</strong> and the Prophet Muhammad (Peace Be Upon Him).</p>
        </section>

        <section id="s3" class="scroll-mt-32 border-t border-slate-100 pt-10 pb-10">
          <h2>III. Verification Pillars in the Online Age</h2>
          <div class="not-prose flex flex-col gap-8 mt-10">
            <div class="flex gap-5 md:gap-6 bg-slate-50 p-6 rounded-3xl border border-slate-100 transition-colors" onmouseover="this.style.borderColor='var(--color-indigo-200)'" onmouseout="this.style.borderColor='transparent'">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center font-black text-lg shrink-0 border" style="background-color: var(--color-indigo-50); color: var(--color-indigo-600); border-color: var(--color-indigo-100)">01</div>
